OL,3,EQUAKE: MISSION PACK 1GPC```````````````
OL,5,BThe first of two officially sanctioned 
OL,6,BQuake add-ons, Mission Pack 1 is       
OL,7,Bsubtitled Scourge of Armagon.          
OL,9,FUnlike most of the Net-lifted          
OL,10,Fcommercially available Quake levels,   
OL,11,Fthe Mission Pack features 15 quality   
OL,12,Fstages, two new monsters, three new    
OL,13,Fweapons and three new power-ups.       
OL,15,BRegretably, there's only a single      
OL,16,BDeathmatch arena, but for solo Quake   
OL,17,Bfanatics this has to be worth          
OL,18,Binvestigating. Warning - the soundtrack
OL,19,Bis pretty cheesy.                      
